wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Á̠ [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|ku fwun ma̠ a̠mgba̠m a̠yaawiki ba]] a̠vwuonswat IP ang ka.'''

A̠tyu wu a̠ fwun wa yet $1 ($2).
Jat ji nang a̠ nwuak ja yet ''$3''.

* Tsa fwun hu: $4
* Tyiai fwun hu: $5

A̠vwuonswat IP ang kya yet $6.
Ma̠sa̠kut mbeang a̠mgba̠m a̠bankhang tazwa na mami a̠mgba̠m lilyip nang a nyia̠ a̠ni.

Ka̠ a nwuak a̠cucuk nyia̠ á̠ fwun ang ma̠ ghyuap wa, da̠ a maai shyia̠ á̠ghyang nkhang ma̠ng tyiet mi̠ kwai fwuo a̠mgba̠m swanta si̠ [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|Á̠ nwai byia̠ á̠gang a̠yaawukili]] hu.
Kalak, ka̠ a cat lyiat tazwa fwun hu ma̠sa̠kut [[m:Steward requests/Global|ta̠m ma̠ng catkyang nyiung mat á̠ bu nwuan ang dyo mi̠ Meta-Wiki]].
